sailpoint.object

Class ManagedResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.object.ManagedResource

  • public class ManagedResource
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to define name mappings for resources. The attribute map is keyed by IdentityIQ attribute name and the value is the target attribute name.

    A list of these will be maintained within the IntegrationConfig, search structures are built at runtime.
